{
  "stem": "4226.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I could have escaped if I wanted to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I don't think my parents could have.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They..",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I could have escaped my own, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very few.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know anybody who, who escaped from that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- they brought train, train carriages.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they started deporting us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was among the first.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a few transports going there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was, I think, in the second.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The first went, and next day, I went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With me together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went-- they, they were Hungarian guards on cattle trains. , and they had only a small window, a small opening, a good strain, with barbed wire over it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the doors were shut.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they tell a story that you're going to-- you won't-- you won't be taken out of the country, and all stories like that, so they wouldn't cause any panic.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But we were taken to a town on the-- Hungarian town which was once Slovakia called Kass-- Kosice-- Kass.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "K-A- double S, or the Czech name now is Kosice, K-O-S-I-C-E.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] at the railway station, they-- we could get off the train, one person, if you had any dish, to collect some water, fresh water, drinking water.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we only stopped for about 15 minutes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they changed the guards there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Hungarians retreated, and the German guards took over, and moved off to, to Birkenau, Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, very full.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only Hungarian Jews.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Romanian Jews were not deported.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They, they, they were not on the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were on a separate-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they had guard, little guard cubicles on the train.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had a carriage-- passenger carriage for the guards only.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For the German guards.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
